  "seniorLabel": "What sounds senior here",
  "seniorBodyText": "Saying ‘the hash is collision-resistant, so signing it is equivalent to signing the content’ — not just ‘I’d sign it’ — is the tell that you understand why hash-then-sign is the standard.",
